About Camber Energy
















Significant Drilling and Development Potential
We are strategically and financially positioned to drill undeveloped locations in prolific basins with predictable results. View Our Assets 






Proven Leadership and Technical Expertise
Our team of industry veterans continues to source opportunistic acquisitions, improve operational and organizational efficiencies, and leverage their knowledge and experience with the latest technologies. View Team  






