Lucas Energy, Inc. (LEI) - Oil & Gas - Deals and Alliances Profile [Updated: 16-12-2016]

Published by Global Data: 16 Dec 2016 | 210799 | In StockSummaryLucas Energy, Inc. (Lucas Energy) is an independent oil and gas company, which carries out the exploration and development of oil and gas assets. It explores for crude oil and natural gas. Its oil and gas reserves are located in three major reservoir areas of interest namely the Eagle Ford Shale, Austin Chalk and Buda zones. The company’s Eagle Ford properties are located within Gonzales, Karnes and Wilson Counties, Texas. It has interests in producing properties and undeveloped acreage in Texas and Oklahoma. The company also has interests in producing shale properties in Glasscock County, Texas. Lucas Energy is headquartered in Houston, Texas, the US.Lucas Energy, Inc. (LEI) - Oil & Gas - Deals and Alliances Profile provides you comprehensive data and trend analysis of the company's Mergers and Acquisitions (M&As), partnerships and financings. The report provides detailed information on Mergers and Acquisitions, Equity/Debt Offerings, Private Equity, Venture Financing and Partnership transactions recorded by the company over a five year period. The report offers detailed comparative data on the number of deals and their value categorized into deal types, sub-sector and regions.GlobalData derived the data presented in this report from proprietary in-house Oil & Gas eTrack deals database, and primary and secondary research.Scope- Financial Deals - Analysis of the company's financial deals including Mergers and Acquisitions, Equity/Debt Offerings, Private Equity, Venture Financing and Partnerships.- Deals by Year - Chart and table displaying information encompassing the number of deals and value reported by the company by year, for a five year period.- Deals by Type - Chart and table depicting information including the number of deals and value reported by the company by type such as Mergers and Acquisitions, Equity/Debt Offering etc.- Deals by Region - Chart and table presenting information on the number